# Contributing to SimonAI

## Dev flow
- Fork â†’ branch â†’ PR to `main`.
- Use conventional commits (e.g., `feat:`, `fix:`, `docs:`).

## Issues & PRs
- Use templates.
- Link to related issues.
- Keep PRs small and focused.

## Style
- Web: Prettier default, ES modules.
- iOS: Swift 5.9+, SwiftLint (in CI).

## Local
- `/web`: open `index.html` or run a simple static server.
- `/ios`: open in Xcode; target iOS 17+.

